{"title":"辛亥革命杂咏","authors":["朱德"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛亥革命杂咏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同盟领袖是中山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清帝推翻民有权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起义武昌全国应"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫除封建几千年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云南起义是重阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下定决心援武昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过多时诸运动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功成一夜好开场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生擒总督李经羲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丧失人心莫敢支"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要投降即免死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出滇礼送亦宜之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靳逃钟死人称快（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举出都督是蔡锷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五华山上树红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出师两路援川鄂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）靳云鹏是当时云南督练公所总参议，起义时逃走。钟麟同是当时第十九镇统制，被击毙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆曾率队到宜宾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举红旗援弟兄（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前军达到自流井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已报成都敌肃清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）当时援川军队是打的红旗，戴红边帽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众争修铁路权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志同道合会全川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排山倒海人民力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起中华革命先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）辛亥五月，四川保路同志会成立，保路运动进入高潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁评论大文章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指出中国革命方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先进亚洲从此始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发扬真理更辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中山革命未完成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党人应运生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶段分明仍不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗三面正高擎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1961年10月7日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}